          "text": "你且听道：你父孙武子，惯用雷炮兴兵，玉帝大怒，用五雷将他击死。他的原\n魂不散，在那九霄云外，飘来飘去。见你母燕丹公主，生得几分姿色，他就降\n下凡来。你乃父投子胎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "败坏纲常！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "近前来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸呸呸！住口！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大骂毛道礼不端，\n不该阵前出恶言！"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "父投子胎纲常乱，\n败坏人伦欺了天！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙膑、毛蕡同开打，同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
