    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "毛蕡",
        "王翦"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四蓝龙套、王翦同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王翦",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辕门战鼓响，儿郎报端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（毛蕡上，吐血。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "毛蕡 （吐） 唔……"
        },
        {
          "character": "王翦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀败了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王翦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何这等模样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被痂夫打了一拐，去了五百年道行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王翦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，免战高悬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，待愚兄摆下五雷大阵擒他！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王翦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那贼惯用五雷伤人，画虎不成，反类其犬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚下摆的阴五雷，那贼摆的阳五雷，有道是“阴能克阳”。当是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王翦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦始皇冠袍带履，可在营中？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王翦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在营中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请至后面。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王翦、四蓝龙套同下。毛蕡烧香，画符，引五雷上。王翦上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "毛蕡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！孙伯龄阴魂前来打阵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙膑上，打阵。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
