    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "为叔的苦仗恶征有三年",
        "孙燕",
        "孙膑",
        "悲切切上青牛肝肠痛断",
        "看过来沉香棍请把礼见",
        "看酒来把为叔活来祭奠",
        "纵有神通难施展",
        "胆战心寒心神乱"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙燕搀孙膑同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三魂飘渺不安然。\n身似筛糠为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，为叔这几日心惊肉跳，坐卧不安，不知为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胆战心寒心神乱、孙燕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待侄儿看来。吓，叔父头上鲜花，哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "妖道设下巧机关，\n将为叔鲜花押阵前。\n要报冤仇难上难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，那妖道摆下五雷大阵，将为叔鲜花，压在阵中了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纵有神通难施展、孙燕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔父就该身背杏黄旗，前去破阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那贼摆的阴五雷，为叔摆的阳五雷，有道是“阴能克阳”，那杏黄旗不能得破！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙燕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔父不去打阵，祖母娘亲，倚靠何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "猛然提起老慈颜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘亲，母亲，娘……"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寸断肝肠泪珠涟。\n两家结下山海冤。\n反将鲜花押阵前。\n亲到阵前走一番。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "准备下杏黄旗、鹅眉剑，\n再备为叔的引魂幡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙膑下。孙燕备牛。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙燕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请叔父！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙膑上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小孙燕在一旁珠泪不干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望扶儿登宝殿，\n恢复燕邦锦江山。\n到如今事事不周全。\n这杯酒送我到鬼门三关。\n此一番全仗你会战军前。\n可叹我入仙山，悟参禅，到如今，为报父仇冤，无有结果收缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙燕！"
        },
        {
          "character": "为叔的苦仗恶征有三年、看酒来把为叔活来祭奠、看过来沉香棍请把礼见、悲切切上青牛肝肠痛断、孙燕",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙膑",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙燕",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔父！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙燕 （同叫头） （儿）（叔父）吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙膑、孙燕同下。）"
        }
      ],
